<li><a href="/wiki/Nikk%C5%8D_T%C5%8Dsh%C5%8D-g%C5%AB" title="Nikkō Tōshō-gū">Nikkō Tōshō-gū</a>, <a href="/wiki/Nikk%C5%8D,_Tochigi" title="Nikkō, Tochigi">Nikkō</a>, <a href="/wiki/Tochigi_Prefecture" title="Tochigi Prefecture">Tochigi Prefecture</a></li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=%C5%8Csaki_Hachiman_Shrine&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ōsaki Hachiman Shrine (page does not exist)">Ōsaki Hachiman Shrine</a>, <a href="/wiki/Miyagi_Prefecture" title="Miyagi Prefecture">Miyagi Prefecture</a></li>
