<li id="cite_note-12"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12" title="">^</a></b> Yamakage, Motohisa "The Essence of Shinto, - Japan's Spiritual Heart, Kodansha International Tokyo 2006, p.12-13; 226.</li>
</ol>
</div>
